person.persName: Austin W. England (Grayson County, Kentucky farm laborer)

body.p: Grayson County, Kentucky farm laborer. Kentucky native. Son of John England and Jane England. Farmer in Grayson County in 1850. Farm laborer in Grayson County in 1860.

bibl.p: Seventh Manuscript Census of the United States (1850), Population Schedules, Kentucky, Grayson County, p. 67. Eighth Manuscript Census of the United States (1860), Population Schedules, Kentucky, Grayson County, p. 102. Ninth Manuscript Census of the United States (1870), Population Schedules, Kentucky, Grayson County, Haynes, p. 23.
